        {
          "type": "reasoning",
          "text": "The user is asking two questions:\n1. Why does PowerShell support multiple profiles?\n2. Why can different programs (hosts) have their own profiles?\n\nI'm in plan/read-only mode, but that's fine - this is just a discussion question, no edits needed.\n\nLet me answer concisely.",
